snippet.title: Sleep Test/sleep_rom (SNES Prototype) - Full Walkthrough (read the description)
snippet.description:
Gameplay - 00:00
Warp Effects -13:15

This weird prototype was found in the same folder as "Super Donkey". It uses the SNES mouse to click objects on screen similar to Mario Paint.

And by "Full Walkthrough", I mean covering EVERYTHING the game has to offer. Even the weird Warp effects thing.

I edited some Yoshi Island songs because the game has any sound at all

This video was rushed, so if you find anything wrong tell me in the comments.

SNES Emulator used: Snes9x
